" The best way I've found of switching between line soft-wrap and showing
" hidden characters.
"
" I designed this myself, here's the latest Gist:
" https://gist.github.com/4210145

function! ListWrapToggle()
	if(&list == 1)
		set nolist
		set wrap
	elseif(&wrap == 1)
		set nowrap
		set list
	else
		set nowrap
		set list
	endif
endfunction

